/**
 * CNSNSS — Polished UI + Clickable AI playlists + Richer Profile + Auth/Profile setup (front-end only)
 * Notes:
 * - No backend: auth/profile is local state + localStorage (demo).
 * - Keeps your overall format/screens; adds polish + a few extra panels.
 */

